folder: Mill Lane & Kings Highway, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Mill Lane, just east of Kings Highway, showing Hendrickson's Store in centre of view, at the N.E. corner of Flatbush Ave., and Kings Highway. At left on the south side of Mill Lane, is the J. Van Wyck house, erected in 1873 and at the right is the J. C. Ryder House, (67 Mill Lane).

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Brooklyn: Mill Lane - Kings Highway
